    * Maze Master  is  not to be  used as an  enticement to purchase another 
      product without the explicit consent of the Publisher, nor is it to be 
      packaged with any other utility or software without such consent.

    * Maze Master is not to be "rented" or leased.

    * A limited license to use this version of Maze Master may only be issued 
      by The Flatirons Group.

    * Disk vendors who charge a distribution fee may do so provided the fee
      does not exceed $12.00.  Vendors must not claim, or imply, that this
